data.description: Come check out this newly listed 7 bedroom, 4 bath, 4800+ square foot home on 2.5+ acres of land. This spacious home features both a front porch and back deck highlighting beautiful views spanning the valley. The main level features an open floor plan which is perfect for entertaining and accommodating large families. The upstairs bonus room would be perfect for a fitness room, game room, homeschooling room or even large office. This property offers a unique advantage in the private access to the basement. This is ideal for guests, extended family or even a rental space for additional income. You don't want to miss this, book a showing now!
